@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(0.87)
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.70) + 0.11) - wp.abs(v1))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.39) - (tmp + 0.60 * v2 + 0.38)) + (0.43 / (v2 + 0.27 + v0 + 0.84)))
    v0 = ((v2 / (v2 + 0.28 * v2 + 0.21)) / (tmp + (tmp + 0.93 / v2 + 0.82)))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = ((v2 - wp.abs(v2 + 0.26)) / 0.30)
    data[tid] = v0
